-       - accented, tilded, umlauted, etc.)
-     - :class:`punc8bit` (non-alphabetic characters in ASCII range
-       128-255 - currency, symbols, superscripts, diacriticals, etc.)
-     - :class:`printables` (any non-whitespace character)
